    {
      "id": "PopularPost288130",
      "post_content": "FLAVOUR OVERLOAD!  \n  \nWhen I first started playing Magic, I searched through weird sets for cards. I got 1 Stone Giant from 3rd edition... for some reason (I was playing a mono-red burn deck... I still don't know why).  \n  \nAnyway, back then, I didn't think much of it. Now, it's practically a Fling... or a Brion Stoutarm, minus the direct damage/immediate sacrifice mechanical. I think the difference in art (Mostly naked Barbarian Giant vs. Goat-Throwing Giant). The \"less toughness\" aspect is soooooo cool!  \n  \nThere's obviously the smart way to use him, like throwing something weak to block something with flying. Throw a [Typhoid Rats](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Typhoid Rats) for epic defence (and... how do you throw an horde of rats???).  \n  \nHowever, throw a [Ball Lightning](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning), and Stone Giant becomes Ryu.",
      "posted_by": "Ferlord",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost288130\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_post\">FLAVOUR OVERLOAD!<br/><br/>When I first started playing Magic, I searched through weird sets for cards. I got 1 Stone Giant from 3rd edition... for some reason (I was playing a mono-red burn deck... I still don't know why).<br/><br/>Anyway, back then, I didn't think much of it. Now, it's practically a Fling... or a Brion Stoutarm, minus the direct damage/immediate sacrifice mechanical. I think the difference in art (Mostly naked Barbarian Giant vs. Goat-Throwing Giant). The \"less toughness\" aspect is soooooo cool!<br/><br/>There's obviously the smart way to use him, like throwing something weak to block something with flying. Throw a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Typhoid Rats\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Typhoid Rats\">Typhoid Rats</a> for epic defence (and... how do you throw an horde of rats???).<br/><br/>However, throw a <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Ball Lightning\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Ball Lightning\">Ball Lightning</a>, and Stone Giant becomes Ryu.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '288130'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy54405\">Ferlord</span>\r\n                                (12/30/2012 10:49:43 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl03_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"2.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"3.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"4.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"5.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/>\n<br/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    \u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<br class=\"clear\"/>\n</div>"
